snippet.title: Magical Delicacy - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Magical Delicacy is a wholesome pixel art platformer. Cook magical delicacies from a vast collection of ingredients in your own shop. Explore an unfamiliar town and deliver tasty treats to the townsfolk. Learn new ways to traverse, discover secrets, and experience a unique witchy world.

⭐ *Wishlist Magical Delicacy on Steam:* https://store.steampowered.com/app/2231190/Magical_Delicacy/
---

Official Website: https://www.magicaldelicacy.com

Follow for updates: https://twitter.com/sKaule

Published by @WhitethornGames
